quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,"Nde kammbaa on yanoyta e ma…ď…ďe …ďe yi'a lette …óen ka …ďadii …ďe, woni √Ďalnde Darngal, geece yeddu…ďe Allah …ďen wayloto …ďawla, …ďe wi'anee ontuma : ko …óum …óoo woni …óa…ď…ďayno…óon yaccinaneede ka aduna."
  67,28,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe fennoo…ďe : Yeetee lam, si Allah ∆īettiti lam, O ∆īettitii gom…óim…ďe wonndu…ďe e am …ďen, wollo O yurmii min ko hommbo da…óndata heefer…ďe …ďen e lette muusu…óe? O alaa da…óndoo- wo mbo e he…óe hay gooto."
  67,29,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe : Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŇčke noddoowo on e rewugol Mo Kanko tun On. Men gom…óinii Mo, ko e Makko tun kadi woni ko men fawata fiyakuuji amen. Aray pellet, nde anndoton, ko hommbo wonunoo e majjere …ďanngunde e wonunoo…ďe e laawol focciingol ngol."
  67,30,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ďee sirkoo…ďe : Yeetee lam, si ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam ka leydi, ko hommbo addanta on ontuma ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam ko ila? Ko Allah tun."
  68,1,"Nuun : Haala fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah. Allah woondirii …óoo karambol, O woondiri kadi ko yim…ďe …ďen winndirta kon karammbi ma…ď…ďe …óin."
  68,2,"Aan Nulaa…óo a wonaa kaangaa…óo, sabu ko Allah neeminir-maa kon Annabaaku. Aan ko a danndii…óo e feetere nde …ďee sirkoo…ďe siforte."
  68,3,"Ko pellet, hino woodan-maa mbarjaari ndi ta∆īondirtaa e ko dokkal hay gooto e dow Ma sabu kon ronnditagol nulal ngal e yim…ďe …ďen."
  68,4,"E ko pellet, hi…óa e jikku mawngu ngu Alqur'aana ardi e mun. Ko a jikkinir…óo ko woni e mayre kon e mbaadi timmundi."
  68,5,"Aray nde tinaa an, …ďee fennoo…ďe kadi yi'a."
  68,6,"√Ďalnde goonga fee√Īata, anndoton ko hommbo e mo'on woni haangaa…óo."
  68,7,"Pellet, ko Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo …ďuri anndude oo√Īii…óo on e laawol Makko ngol, ko Kanko kadi …ďuri anndude feewu…ďe …ďen. Himo anndi ko kam…ďe woni majju…ďe …ďen, an woni feewu…óo e laawol Makko ngol."
  68,8,"An Nulaa…óo, wata a tewto fennoo…ďe ko addu…óaa kon."
  68,9,"Hi…ďe yi…ói si a newantono …ďe e innde diina, kam…ďe kadi …ďe newano-maa."
  68,10,"Wata a tewto kadi kala …óuu…óu…óo woondirgol meere, hoy…óo."
  68,11,"∆äuu…óu…óo √Īo'ugol yim…ďe, …óuu…óu…óo yaarugol waddude yim…ďe fii senndira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe."
  68,12,"∆äuu…óu…óo ha…óugol mo∆ī∆īere, jaggitoowo jawle e teddule e pittaali yim…ďe, …óuu…óu…óo bakkaatu e geddi."
  68,13,"Yoora-…ďerndeejo, Ňči√Īiraa…óo he…ďireede nii."
  68,14,"Fii tun o wonii jom jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe, o townitanii gom…óingol Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on."
  68,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen …óen janngaama e makko, o wi'a: Ko tinndi adinoo…ďe nii."